Subject: Re: [T2] help me remove my head

Air injection system or pushrod tubes?

If it is pushrod tubes grab each tube gently with some slip joint pliers 
and twist back and forth with a gentle pull away from the engine block and 
they will slide right out.

Replace those seals when you assemble it.


